text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gunk Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Glutownica</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Medium-range Biochemical attack</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak biochemiczny średniego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BATTLE_VOMIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Battle Vomit</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Torsjostrzał</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BATTLE_VOMIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Short-range Biochemical area of effect attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemiczny atak obszarowy krótkiego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_SPIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gunk Spit</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Glutopluj</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_SPIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Medium-range Biochemical attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak biochemiczny średniego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIOCHEMICAL_DISCHARGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical Discharge</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wyładowanie biochemiczne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIOCHEMICAL_DISCHARGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Discharges a torrent of biochemicals at short range, dealing high damage.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zasypuje przeciwnika gradem pocisków biochemicznych z niewielkiej odległości, zadając poważne obrażenia.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIOCHEMICAL_BARRAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical Barrage</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ostrzał biochemiczny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIOCHEMICAL_BARRAGE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a repeating barrage of Biochemicals at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu wieloma seriami pocisków biochemicznych.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CAUSTIC_SMOKE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Caustic Smoke</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żrący dym</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CAUSTIC_SMOKE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cover a {hexradius} hex radius area with an acid cloud that melts armor and deals damage.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pokrywa obszar o promieniu {hexradius} pól chmurą kwasu, który roztwarza pancerz i zadaje obrażenia.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ACIDIC_INFUSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Acidic Composite</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kwasowa mieszanka</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ACIDIC_INFUSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Attacks from Biochemical weapons are infused with acid, giving [abilityred]Melt Armor[/abilityred], removing {armorMelt}[armor/] with each hit.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Amunicja do broni biochemicznej zostaje nasycona kwasem, dzięki czemu [abilityred]topi pancerz[/abilityred], usuwając przy każdym trafieniu {armorMelt}[armor/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ION_CONDUCTIVE_INFUSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Infusion: Ionic</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Nasycenie jonowe</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ION_CONDUCTIVE_INFUSION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Attacks from Biochemical Weapons now deal Arc damage and have a 12[strengthWave/] strength chance (8[strengthwave/] for repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Electrified[/abilityred] to non-Ethereal units for 3[turn/].[br/][br/]Only one Infusion can be active at a time.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki bronią biochemiczną zadają teraz obrażenia elektryczne i mają szansę (siła 12[strengthWave/], 8[strengthwave/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]porażenia[/abilityred] u jednostek nieeterycznych na 3[turn/] .[br/][br/]W danej chwili może być aktywne tylko jedno nasycenie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CEREBRAL_STRAIN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cerebral Strain</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szczep mózgowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CEREBRAL_STRAIN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical attacks deal +{extradamage} damage against non-Mindless units and have a {CatatonicChance}[StrengthPsyche/] strength chance ({CatatonicChanceRepeating}[StrengthPsyche/] on repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Catatonic[/abilityred] to non-Mindless units with Psionic or Entropy abilities for {CatatonicTurn}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki biochemiczne zadają +{extradamage} pkt. obrażeń jednostkom nienależącym do bezmózgich i mają szansę (siła {CatatonicChance}[StrengthPsyche/], {CatatonicChanceRepeating}[StrengthPsyche/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) wywołania [abilityred]katatonii[/abilityred] na {CatatonicTurn}[turn/] u jednostek nienależących do bezmózgich i posługujących się psioniką lub entropią.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CEREBRAL_STRAIN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{CerebralDamage} extra damage against non-Mindless units and {CerebralChance}[strengthpsyche/] strength chance to apply [abilityred]Catatonic[/abilityred] to non-Mindless Psionic/Entropic units for {CerebralTurn}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Dodatkowe {CerebralDamage} pkt. obrażeń przeciwko jednostkom nienależącym do bezmózgich i szansa o sile {CerebralChance}[strengthpsyche/] wywołania [abilityred]katatonii[/abilityred] u jednostek psionicznych/entropicznych nienależących do bezmózgich na {CerebralTurn}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VISCOUS_COMPOSITE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Viscous Strain</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Lepki szczep</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">VISCOUS_COMPOSITE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical attacks have a {SlowChanceSingle}[strengthBio/] strength chance ({SlowChanceRepeating}[StrengthBio/] on repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Slow[/abilityred] to non-Ethereal units for {ViscousTurn}[turn/].[br/][br/]If a unit is already [abilityred]Slowed[/abilityred], that unit has a {ImmobilizeChanceSingle}[StrengthBio/] strength chance ({ImmobilizeChanceRepeating}[StrengthBio/] on repeating attacks) to become [abilityred]Immobilize[/abilityred] for {ImmobilizeDuration}[turn/].</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki biochemiczne mają szansę (siła {SlowChanceSingle}[strengthBio/], {SlowChanceRepeating}[StrengthBio/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) na spowodowanie [abilityred]spowolnienia[/abilityred] u jednostek nieeterycznych na {ViscousTurn}[turn/].[br/][br/]Jeśli dana jednostka jest już [abilityred]spowolniona[/abilityred], ma szansę (siła {ImmobilizeChanceSingle}[StrengthBio/], {ImmobilizeChanceRepeating}[StrengthBio/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) na [abilityred]paraliż[/abilityred] na {ImmobilizeDuration}[turn/].</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_BRINGER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blight Bringer</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zwiastun plagi</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_BRINGER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Unit gains +{IncreasedResistanceBio}[damageBio/] resistance and Immunity to [abilityblue]Biochemical Status Effects and Hazards[/abilityblue].[br/]At the end of this unit's turn, enemy non-Ethereal units within {BlightRadiusHex} hexes have a {BlightBringerChance} strength chance to gain [abilityred]Blighted [/abilityred] for {BlightTurns}.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostka uzyskuje +{IncreasedResistanceBio}[damageBio/] do odporności i niewrażliwość na [abilityblue]biochemiczne efekty stanu i zagrożenia[/abilityblue].[br/]Na zakończenie tury tej jednostki wrogie jednostki nieeteryczne w promieniu {BlightRadiusHex} pól będą mieć szansę (siła {BlightBringerChance}) na zapadnięcie na [abilityred]zarazę morową[/abilityred] na {BlightTurns}.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_INFECTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blightworm Injector</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Iniektor morosiemców</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_INFECTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{BlightParasitesChance}[strengthbio/] strength chance to apply [abilityred]Blightworm Infestation[/abilityred] to units until the end of combat.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szansa (siła {BlightParasitesChance}[strengthbio/]) na wywołanie [abilityred]zakażenia morosiemcem[/abilityred] u jednostek do końca walki.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_INFECTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical attacks have a {BlightWormChance}[strengthbio/] strength chance ({BlightWormChanceRepeating}[strengthbio/] for repeating attacks) to apply [abilityred]Blightworm Infestation[/abilityred] to units until end of combat. A unit infected will explode in a {HexRadius} hex radius when it dies, dealing {BiochemicalDamage}[damagebio/] to all units in the explosion, except for those using this mod.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ataki biochemiczne mają szansę (siła {BlightWormChance}[strengthbio/], {BlightWormChanceRepeating}[strengthbio/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) na wywołanie [abilityred]zakażenia morosiemcem[/abilityred] u jednostek do końca walki. Zarażona w ten sposób jednostka eksploduje w chwili śmierci, zadając {BiochemicalDamage}[damagebio/] wszystkim jednostkom w promieniu {HexRadius} pól (z wyjątkiem jednostek używających iniektora).</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_INFECTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEBUFF_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blightworm Infestation</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zakażenie morosiemcem</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLIGHT_INFECTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEBUFF_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit is infected by a Blightworm infection until end of combat. If the unit dies, it will explode in a {HexRadius} hex radius, dealing {BiochemicalDamage} to all units caught in the explosion, except for those with the Blightworm Infestation unit mod.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ta jednostka do końca walki odczuwa efekty zakażenia morosiemcem. Jeśli zginie, eksploduje zadając {BiochemicalDamage} wszystkim jednostkom w promieniu {HexRadius} pól (z wyjątkiem jednostek używających iniektora).</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">THRAX_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Thrax Rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Karabin morowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">THRAX_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A medium-range Biochemical attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak biochemiczny średniego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">THRAX_BLASTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Thrax Pistol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistolet morowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">THRAX_BLASTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A low damage, short-range Biochemical attack.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak biochemiczny krótkiego zasięgu zadający niewielkie obrażenia.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_THROWER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gunk Thrower</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Glutomiot</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GUNK_THROWER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shoot a glob of Biochemical matter at medium range.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wystrzeliwuje kulę materii biochemicznej; broń średniego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CORROSIVE_BILE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Corrosive Bile</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Żrąca żółć</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CORROSIVE_BILE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spit armor melting Biochemicals at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pluje w cel substancją biochemiczną roztwarzającą pancerz.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WAX_CEMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wax Cement</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tężejąca żółć</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WAX_CEMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vomit a quick-hardening bile on the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wymiotuje na cel błyskawicznie twardniejącą żółcią.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TOXIN_SPIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Toxin Spit</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Toksyczna ślina</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TOXIN_SPIT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spit a highly poisonous blob of toxic vomit at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pluje w cel kulą silnie trujących wymiotów.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CEMENTING_SPRAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Cementing Spray</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Tężejąca mgiełka</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">CEMENTING_SPRAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vomit a hardening Biochemical mix on the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wymiotuje na cel twardniejącą mieszankę biochemiczną.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_ARROW</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bio Arrows</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biostrzały</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_ARROW</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire arrows with Biochemical tips at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Razi cel strzałami wyposażonymi w biochemiczne groty.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_BLASTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire Bio Blaster</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzał z biomiotacza</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_BLASTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Biochemical round at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu pociskiem biochemicznym.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_SHELL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bio Shell Bombardment</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ostrzał biopociskami</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_SHELL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Launch a series of Biochemical shells at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ostrzeliwuje cel serią pocisków biochemicznych.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bio Cannon</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działo biochemiczne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a mounted cannon filled with Biochemical mass at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Odpala działo pokładowe uderzające w cel biochemiczną masą.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_BLASTER</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bio Blaster</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Miotacz biochemiczny</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">HUNTING_BOW</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Hunting Bow</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Łuk myśliwski</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POISON_ARROWS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Poison Arrows</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zatrute strzały</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POISON_ARROWS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire arrows with Poisoned tips at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Razi cel strzałami wyposażonymi w zatrute groty.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_VAPOR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Biochemical Vaporizer</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wyparka biochemiczna</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BIO_VAPOR</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a slew of vaporized chemicals, damaging any mater